quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,121,"Mi teff$ev, รปรปbeรช zik, si twacult ik, temmalev i lmumnin imukan umennu$, ร–ebbi Issel, d Amusnaw"
  3,122,"Mi qรดib feclent snat n trebbuyaรข nnwen, u ร–ebbi d Bab nnsent. Iwata i yal lmumen, ad ippkel $ef ร–ebbi"
  3,123,"Ni$ Iรขiwen ikwen ร–ebbi di Badรด, mi tellam tendellem. Ihi, รชezzbet i ร–ebbi, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  3,124,"Mi tenniv i lmumnin: \"day ur testeqnaรขm ara, mi kwen Iรขiwen ร–ebbi s krav igima n lmalayek, id irsen"
  3,125,"Xaรฎi, ma tรปebรดem u tรชezzbem, ma $ewwsen d fellawen, a kwen Iรขiwen Mass nnwen, s smus igima n lmalayek ikkaten"
  3,126,"Ur Iga akka ร–ebbi, siwa i ubecceรด nnwen, ad rtiรชen yis wulawen nnwen. Rrbeรช s$uรด ร–ebbi kan, Uzmir, Bab n รปรปwab"
  3,127,"Iwakken ad Iรดรฉ arbaรข n wid ijehlen, ne$ a ten Iรฉรฉaรข, ad u$alen nne$wnin"
  3,128,"Ur k iaรขna lameรด s wacemma. Ad asen Issuref, ne$ a ten Iรขaqeb, nitni d imednas"
  3,129,"N ร–ebbi i illan deg igenwan, i illan di tmurt. Ipsemmiรช i win i S ihwan. Ipรขaqab win i S ihwan. ร–ebbi Ipsemmiรช, Ipรชunu"